data.description: PERFECT HOME for the first time buyer.  Walking distance to Elem/Middle/High school.  Spacious back yard offers great privacy. Paved RV pkg to the side of carport - or- could be a wonderful outdoor entertainment area.  Large eat-in kitchen with ample cabinets + a pantry closet.  Complete  Interior repainted.  Carpet replacement in LR & Master BR in progress..  Some exterior clean up in progress.  Master BR has a half bath. HVAC System replaced last year.  Gas (instant) heat and gas (cost saving) hot water heater.  Really cute All Brick home.  Easy flow floor plan.  Perfect Location!  Currently the only home for sale in this very desirable sidewalk neighborhood.  Beautiful beaches less than 5 minutes away.  Waterfront park on the Sound w/boat launch 1 minute away. Home offered ''as is''.
